## BEGIN Force to HTTPS (skip for localhost)
<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On
    # Jangan paksa HTTPS untuk host localhost (pengembangan lokal)
    RewriteCond %{HTTP_HOST} !^localhost(:[0-9]+)?$ [NC]
    RewriteCond %{HTTPS} off
    RewriteRule ^(.*)$ https://%{HTTP_HOST}%{REQUEST_URI} [L,R=301]
</IfModule>
## END Force to HTTPS

## CORS dikelola oleh Laravel (config/cors.php). Jangan set header CORS di sini.
## Jika sebelumnya ada Header always set Access-Control-Allow-*, harap dihapus.

<IfModule mod_rewrite.c>
    RewriteEngine On
    # Aturan ini penting untuk Laravel, JANGAN DIUBAH
    RewriteRule ^(.*)$ public/$1 [L]
</IfModule>